  "commit_message": "Harden the @sigstore/core ASN.1/DER parser (#1678)\n\nAdd a set of strictness and robustness checks to the hand-rolled DER\nparser used to parse X.509 certificates and RFC 3161 timestamps, without\nchanging any public interfaces.\n\n- Add a recursion-depth limit to the parse/collectSubs mutual recursion\n- Use BigInt accumulation for OID arcs to avoid 32-bit truncation\n- Enforce minimal (canonical) DER length encodings\n- Accept only canonical BOOLEAN values (0x00/0xff)\n- Reject top-level trailing data ",
